title: Creative Furniture Theo Design Modern Elegant Reception Desk with Pedestal in Wooden Laminate Finish
description:
The Theo Design by Creative Furniture. This Reception Desk is one of the popular reception table within the Creative Furniture catalog.

The front reception panel has horizontal panels giving the table a rich look as a first impression of the reception counter. The top panel for receiving visitors is wide enough for signing with any reception pen or keeping a reception bell to alert new customers.
editorContent:
The Theo Design by Creative Furniture. This Reception Desk is one of the popular reception table within the Creative Furniture catalog.


The front reception panel has horizontal panels giving the table a rich look as a first impression of the reception counter. The top panel for receiving visitors is wide enough for signing with any reception pen or keeping a reception bell to alert new customers.


This modern reception centerpiece comes with a 3-drawer cabinet with wheels with a lock, to store files, and other important documents or company office related items. The reception counter has good height , so that the receptionist can sit on the reception chair and have a good view of incoming visitors.This modern table comes in Wooden Laminate Finish along with High-Pressure Laminated Sheet with a marble appearance and will make any office stand out and give all the customers a strong and solid first impression. If you are looking for an eye-catching reception desk do not look any further.Assuring endurance and sturdiness crafted from robust Egger / Emilam / Danube Boards.Make sure the finish is determined after the design selection.You may pick any single wood finish for this product from the color spectrum below.The other solid hue will remain as illustrated in the picture.The wires are pulled into the panel legs to create a completely clutter-free tabletop and provide more productive work area.Design your custom furniture with ease from our selection module.Simple maintenance for functional preservation.

The Strip Series by Creative Furniture. This Luxury Bedroom Upholstered Double Bed with 2 Bed Side Tables. for Adults and Children friendly is very popular within the Creative Furniture catalog.Choose this Upholstered Double bed to add some functional and royality to your private bedroom space. Featuring a precisely crafted designer bed with an elegant finish.

A roomy upholstered storage means complete comfort. Our large Double Bed add rustic warmth to the design of your couple room and are suitable for both children and adults.This piece has a strong foundation and a stable design in Solid Wood leg brace and adds a refined touch to your private bedroom space in with Velvet Upholstery

Assuring endurance and sturdiness crafted from solid wood, finished with natural polish and cladded with high resilience foam covered in a sheet of Dacron fiber.

You may pick any single upholstery fabric for this product from the color spectrum below.Design your custom furniture with ease from our selection module.Avoid Using any heavy chemicals or Acidic solutions over the upholstery for cleaning purpose.

The bed-side table + mattress are not-included in the price; they are sold separately on the website.

Simple maintenance for functional preservation.
